<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="15Feb1925"><font color="red">15 February 1925</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver from Lucia Joyce): Dr Borsch says [the conjunctivitis] will go in four or five days and then he will operate. My father &hellip; sends you inclosed a photograph of Leopold Bloom&apos;s house in Dublin now a small grocery shop &hellip; I think Mr McAlmon will bring you [the disc] and the MS. </div>
